How to create Animation GIF with TMPGEnc Video Mastering Works 7
New Project (Normal mode)
Add Slideshow
on Add Slideshow window
  Image Settings > Add images : add material images
  Image Settings > Global Settings > Basic Settings > Time : set to 1 second
  Filter > Speed : switch speed to on and adjust the play speed
  OK
Output Setting : select Animation image file output and adjust size and fps
Encode
